## Hotel Analysis Dashboard

This Power BI dashboard provides a comprehensive analysis of hotel performance, focusing on occupancy, revenue generation, booking trends, and overall business performance. The report is organized into multiple analytical views, including an overall performance dashboard, monthly trend analysis, and revenue-focused insights.

Users can explore key hotel metrics through interactive filters and visualizations to understand seasonal demand patterns, compare performance across different periods, and evaluate revenue contributions. The Monthly Analysis page highlights changes in business performance over time, while the Revenue Basis section provides a detailed breakdown of revenue drivers and financial performance indicators.

Overall, the dashboard helps hotel managers and stakeholders monitor operational efficiency, identify revenue opportunities, track performance trends, and make data-driven decisions to improve profitability and guest service outcomes.
